60
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:23,590
They became ghost districts,
challenges to urban development.

61
00:04:23,590 --> 00:04:27,530
Many cities looked for new uses for empty
inner-city ports.

62
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:30,920
Filled with industrial structures and industrial
