focused on preserving traditional port infrastructure

68
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:55,730
and recovering the water for locals.

69
00:04:55,730 --> 00:05:01,080
Baltimore chose to redevelop the waterfront
for leisure and tourism,

70
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:06,960
a project that was then exported to other
port cities around the world.

71
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:12,860
The London Docklands controversially redeveloped
an industrial waterfront into office spaces

